# {{PROJECT_NAME}}

Actor-RTC Web project using Service Worker + WASM architecture.

## Quick Start

```bash
# Install dependencies
npm install

# Generate code from proto definitions
actr gen -l web

# Build WASM
cd wasm && bash build.sh && cd ..

# Start dev server
npm run dev
```

## Architecture

```
{{PROJECT_NAME}}/
├── Actr.toml              # Actor configuration
├── package.json           # Node.js dependencies
├── vite.config.ts         # Vite dev server config
├── index.html             # Entry HTML page
├── protos/                # Protocol buffer definitions
│   ├── local/             # Local service definitions
│   └── remote/            # Remote service definitions
├── src/
│   ├── main.ts            # Application entry point
│   └── generated/         # Auto-generated code (actr gen)
│       ├── actr-config.ts # Configuration from Actr.toml
│       ├── index.ts       # Re-exports
│       └── *.actorref.ts  # Typed RPC wrappers
├── wasm/                  # Rust WASM crate
│   ├── Cargo.toml
│   ├── build.sh
│   └── src/
│       ├── lib.rs         # WASM entry + service handler registration
│       └── generated/     # Proto-generated Rust types
└── public/
    └── actor.sw.js        # Service Worker entry (generated)
```
